PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company for a term of three years. (PURDY CRAWFORD, Westmount, Quebec, in the place of Maurice Mayer, who has resigned; JEAN B. FOREST, Edmonton, Alberta, in the place of Eugene Demkiw, whose term has expired; and EDWARD PETER NEUFELD, Mississauga, Ontario, in the place of George W. Wickett, who has resigned)
